data.title: Nicky Wu
data.meta_description: Nicky Wu (吳奇隆); Taiwanese; Nicky Wu is a Taiwanese singer and actor born in Xinzhuang, Taipei, Taiwan, with ancestral roots in Fujian. He debuted in 1988
